om/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/TheCure_018-1068x678.jpg 1068w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/02/TheCure_018-1920x1219.jpg 1920w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>粉丝们一直猜测<a href="/artists/The-Cure">The Cure</a>可能会在乐队更改社交媒体徽标并更新网站以及披露乐队成员及其亲属的帖子后暗示即将回归音乐。</p><ul class="post-content-read-more"><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/big-reads/the-cure-interview-robert-smith-big-read-exclusive-interview-glastonbury-40th-anniversary-2019-glastonbury-mad-cool-2524439">封面——罗伯特·史密斯 (Robert Smith) 畅谈 The Cure 40 周年</a></strong></li></ul><p>今天（9 月 9 日）早些时候，The Cure 在他们的官方社交媒体页面上将之前的个人资料照片换成了一张新照片，其中包含全黑背景的全新乐队徽标。照片的突然变化让粉丝们相信罗伯特·史密斯和他的同事可能会宣布某种回归——他们希望这就是期待已久的《失落世界之歌》。</p><p>粉丝们很快就在乐队 Facebook 更新下的评论部分分享了他们的兴奋之情。一位用户写道：“请让它终于宣布新专辑！！”，另一位用户则分享道：“来吧，先生们，宣布新专辑！我希望我们能尽快完成新的巡演！”</p><p>另一位粉丝写道：“来吧，新专辑。我想听听你在 2022 年利兹演奏的那些新歌的录音室版本。”他们指的是<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-cure-debut-heartfelt-new-song-a-fragile-thing-in-italy-3343340">《A Fragile Thing》</a> 、《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-cure-debut-new-song-another-happy-birthday-on-north-american-tour-3447557">An Another Happybirthday</a> 》和《 <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-the-cure-debut-another-devastating-new-song-i-can-never-say-goodbye-3332974">I Can Never Say Goodbye</a> 》等歌曲，这是乐队在 2022 年巡演时首次亮相的三首新歌。</p><p>不仅如此，吉他手 Reeves Gabrels 还分享了一个链接，引导歌迷访问乐队<a href="https://www.thecure.com/?fbclid=IwY2xjawFMBHFleHRuA2FlbQIxMAABHWYVCFTL51yoq0ngOgA199AwIVG5bXnOEI8DyHAt_N3xuigzyfSFEXbRGQ_aem__nYh467Rd5R9osJpEbC2Cw" target="_blank" rel="noopener">重新设计的网站</a>，并敦促他们注册邮件列表。贝斯手西蒙·盖洛普（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cures-simon-gallup-forced-to-pull-out-of-japan-show-his-son-replaces-him-on-bass-2533096">在 2019 年的一系列约会中代替父亲参加演出</a>）的儿子伊登也发布了新歌《Alone》的歌词，让歌迷们兴奋不已：“<em>这是我们唱的每首歌的结尾……</em> ” <br /><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/post.php?href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fthecure%2Fposts%2F2014854958930647%3A2014854958930647&amp;show_text=true&amp;width=500" width="500" height="290" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe></p><div id="fb-root"></div><p><script async="1" defer="1" crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/sdk.js#xfbml=1&amp;version=v20.0" nonce="383EEzXh"></script></p><div class="fb-post" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/reevesguitar/posts/pfbid022s6xHb8Kj3ciLAnB6R1HPDv8mytFZh9PWNZHEtWr62wmhA63dnBdH5xwbWiknVf7l?__cft__%5B0%5D=AZWpYgEqUHC9JJdm93d7Cw6f4J2sL5VWPO1GMZpQcoBgabhB-iWTiEud5SQrsxZ4CWDsHascTwjkqnZIQiYPGFMM-CfHj549_1xHVbmNy2ujtFHTrc-iz7kaVaqImWwLrm-kF6blml8iioiXUmlSpvKBT13Y_OhHWhBGkTZ_EY3iOtry0pUnNWh9fNU1eZ_OS6xnGDqmJCAoIyxX7KJjvBT_z19q6bos1IUjXRYjtgFZFwDLafYuKY4OqcDYKI1Nx8s&amp;__tn__=%2CO%2CP-R" data-width="696"><blockquote cite="https://graph.facebook.com/100047358181757/posts/1043478280574102/" class="fb-xfbml-parse-ignore"><p> The Cure 网站：新闻注册链接 — www.thecure.com</p><p>发布者： <a href="https://www.facebook.com/reevesguitar">Reeves Gabrels</a>于<a href="https://graph.facebook.com/100047358181757/posts/1043478280574102/">2024 年 9 月 9 日星期一</a></p></blockquote></div><div id="fb-root"></div><p><script async="1" defer="1" crossorigin="anonymous" src="https://connect.facebook.net/en_US/sdk.js#xfbml=1&amp;version=v20.0" nonce="P4P9gZCv"></script></p><div class="fb-post" data-href="https://www.facebook.com/edvendetta/posts/pfbid02nXgjXTRvck9ixqjvrnwXixvXwds6DKpefXLyxvmrDVN26PPTyrvah14e7kd7hnbwl?__cft__%5B0%5D=AZXUWC4wyx2CTGO_z4we9h5lsVfZ7sUVEH3lF4gQIwtismMTg3f_ZJbMSW0lbY45h8X8q5lI-5r849TYztgXzZgijDgIg1294Ek8dZuhIXr_3Wt0vxqjAkJ-JvuB_Q9mqc3EdYhoUXKzJVzuxL1wPC8YXzgbHGJ3ONhBsc6YSgVJRKYgSkyDpMVfrA3totRQ8I2E3KK86nJ86r9c8yfeFFl9&amp;__tn__=%2CO%2CP-R" data-width="696"><blockquote cite="https://graph.facebook.com/100060537856765/posts/1062854685742450/" class="fb-xfbml-parse-ignore"><p>这是我们唱的每首歌的结尾......</p><p>发布者：<a href="https://www.facebook.com/edvendetta">伊登·盖洛普 (Eden Gallup)</a>于<a href="https://graph.facebook.com/100060537856765/posts/1062854685742450/">2024 年 9 月 9 日星期一</a></p></blockquote></div><p>这一消息是在<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/the-cure-releas-two-brand-new-songs-as-live-recordings-double-a-side-for-climate-charity-3788702">乐队的两首新歌现场录制发行之前发布的，这首歌曲将成为气候慈善机构“Earth Percent”的双 A 面歌曲</a>。</p><p>通过<a href="https://nakedrecordclub.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">Naked Record Club</a> （一家发行可持续黑胶限量版唱片的唱片公司）发行的《The Cure – Novembre：Live in France 2022》是一首双 A-Side 12 英寸生态黑胶单曲，包含两首在可持续黑胶唱片上录制的现场曲目。<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/live/the-cure-wembley-arena-review-photos-setlist-3365275">乐队“Shows Of A Lost World”巡演的</a>法国站。</p><p>第一首歌曲“And Nothing Is Forever”于 2022 年 11 月 8 日在蒙彼利埃的法国南部竞技场现场录制，而“I Can Never Say Goodbye”则于 2022 年 11 月 13 日在图卢兹 Zénith 现场录制。 The Cure 16 年来首张新曲目。 </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/p/Cl4fTVAKM9u/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xli